            <img src="~/Content/images/corosal3.png" alt="Third slide">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>Panel Lawyer and Legal Advisor</h1>
                    <p>He is Senior Advocate at Civil Court Lucknow. He is Legal Advisor of various nationalised banks in india.</p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="LegalAdvice" role="button">Legal Advice</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
